---

<MainLayout title="10 Best VPN Services of December 2025 | Expert Reviews | Screened" description="Compare the best VPN services including NordVPN, ExpressVPN, and Surfshark. Expert reviews of speed, security, streaming, and privacy features.">
  <!-- Schema Markup -->
