  <!-- Buying Guide -->
  <section id="guide" class="bg-[#F7F8FA] py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-sora text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#162433] mb-6">VPN Buying Guide</h2>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h3 class="font-sora text-xl font-bold text-[#162433] mt-8 mb-4">What to Look for in a VPN</h3>
        <p class="text-[#68727C] mb-4">When choosing a VPN, prioritize these factors:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#68727C]">
          <li><strong>Speed:</strong> Look for VPNs with WireGuard or proprietary fast protocols</li>
          <li><strong>Security:</strong> AES-256 encryption, kill switch, and DNS leak protection are essential</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> Choose providers with audited no-logs policies outside 14 Eyes countries</li>
          <li><strong>Server Network:</strong> More servers = better speeds and more unblocking options</li>
          <li><strong>Device Support:</strong> Ensure apps exist for all your devices</li>
        </ul>

