        <p class="text-[#68727C] mb-4">Our testing methodology includes:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#68727C]">
          <li>Speed tests across 20+ server locations</li>
          <li>Streaming tests with Netflix, Disney+, BBC iPlayer, and more</li>
          <li>Security audits and DNS/WebRTC leak testing</li>
          <li>Real-world usage testing over 30+ days</li>
          <li>Customer support responsiveness checks</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-sora text-xl font-bold text-[#162433] mt-8 mb-4">Free vs Paid VPNs</h3>
        <p class="text-[#68727C]">Free VPNs often monetize through ads or selling data. If you need a free option, ProtonVPN's free tier is the only one we recommend. For full protection, speeds, and streaming access, paid VPNs are worth the $3-7/month investment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
